<li id="cite_note-143"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-143">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFOuazadRancière2012" class="citation web cs1">Ouazad, Amine; Rancière, Romain (March 16, 2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://cepr.org/voxeu/columns/did-mortgage-credit-boom-contribute-decline-us-racial-segregation">"Did the mortgage credit boom contribute to the decline in US racial segregation?"</a>. <i>VoxEU</i>. <a href="/wiki/Centre_for_Economic_Policy_Research" title="Centre for Economic Policy Research">Centre for Economic Policy Research</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20120519175908/http://www.voxeu.org/index.php?q=node/7729">Archived</a> from the original on May 19, 2012<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">November 28,</span> 2023</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=VoxEU&amp;rft.atitle=Did+the+mortgage+credit+boom+contribute+to+the+decline+in+US+racial+segregation%3F&amp;rft.date=2012-03-16&amp;rft.aulast=Ouazad&amp;rft.aufirst=Amine&amp;rft.au=Ranci%C3%A8re%2C+Romain&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fcepr.org%2Fvoxeu%2Fcolumns%2Fdid-mortgage-credit-boom-contribute-decline-us-racial-segregation&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ARacial+segregation+in+the+United+States" class="Z3988"></span></span>
